{"title":"悼谭政同志","authors":["莫文骅"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":11,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"悼谭政同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫文骅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"政工一权威，今日将星颓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兵营均震撼，将士泪珠垂！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六十多载功，闪闪耀光辉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟业群景仰，励志急追随。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"位尊气不骄，哺育使唇焦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决策躬自践，言传又身教。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清风拂两袖，囊中缺钱钞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"源洁水不浊，形端影亦高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"豺狼施暴行，受害极伤心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伤心实伤脑，伤脑折磨人！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哀哉辞世逝，甘棠有遗音。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吾侪如公德，党业必勃兴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1988年11月6日晚于北京301医院"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}